Description: Open Discovery Space intends to facilitate of the implementation of the Action 68 of the Digital Agenda for Europe and to effectively modernize education in the EU- for all subjects and skills. For this- Open Discovery Space aims to unleash the innovation potential of Europe in the production of novel educational and training activities through efficient use of ICT combined with effective stakeholder engagement. Stakeholders to be engaged in the Open Discovery Space innovation generation process include students- teachers- parents- policy makers- and- where appropriate- vendors of eLearning resources.
